---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/navbar.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

import profileImg from "../images/me-architect.jpg";
import labImg from "../images/bass-lab.webp";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <Navbar />
  <div class="pt-20 md:pt-24 px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <header class="relative text-left py-16 md:py-20">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/65 backdrop-blur-2xl border-b border-violet-100/50"></div>
        <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
          <p class="text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-indigo-700/90 mb-4">
            Systems of the Heart, Sound & Code
          </p>
          <h1 class="text-[2.4rem] md:text-[3.1rem] leading-tight font-semibold text-indigo-950/90 drop-shadow-sm">
            JoySomatic
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/85 max-w-none">
            Decoding the language of the Body, Relationships, and Systems through somatics, sound, and engineering.
          </p>
        </div>
      </header>

      <main class="pb-16">
        <section id="about" class="mt-12 md:mt-16">
          <h2 class="inline-block text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-indigo-950/90 border-b border-pink-200 pb-1">
            Hi, I’m José.
          </h2>

          <div class="mt-8 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/90 leading-relaxed">
            <div class="md:float-right md:ml-10 mb-8 w-full md:w-72 lg:w-80 aspect-square relative group">
              <div class="absolute -inset-1.5 bg-gradient-to-tr from-pink-200 to-violet-300 rounded-3xl blur opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-50 transition duration-700"></div>
              <div class="relative h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/40 shadow-xl">
                <Image src={profileImg} alt="José Oñate" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" />
              </div>
            </div>

            <p class="mb-6">
              I look at life through two lenses: the somatic heart that feels the rhythm, and the engineer’s mind that understands the system. My journey has been a lifelong exploration of finding the signal in the noise, whether in a piece of code or a human emotion.
            </p>

            <p class="mb-6">
              Since 2007, I have been deeply immersed in sound engineering, and since 2015, I have applied that same precision to software development. These technical roots provide the foundation for my somatic practice, allowing me to approach human connection and nervous system regulation with the clarity of a systems architect.
            </p>

            <p class="mb-6">
              As a highly sensitive person, I have spent decades navigating the world through therapy, somatic practices, and lived experience. My current focus is a synthesis of technical skill and deep human study—integrating insights from psychology, Internal Family Systems (IFS), meditation, and trauma-informed care to help others find their own resonance.
            </p>

            <div class="clear-both"></div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="relationships" class="mt-12 md:mt-16">
          <h2 class="inline-block text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-indigo-950/90 border-b border-pink-200 pb-1">
            Relationship & Somatic Coaching
          </h2>

          <p class="mt-6 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/90">
            My primary energy is dedicated to helping people navigate the complexities of human connection. I help individuals and couples debug the patterns that keep them stuck, using the body as our primary source of truth.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-8 space-y-4 md:space-y-6">
            <div class="rounded-[2.25rem] bg-white/90 shadow-[0_18px_45px_rgba(148,163,184,0.5)] px-5 py-5">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-950/90">Relational Insight</h3>
              <p class="mt-2.5 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/85">
                We look at the system of your relationship. I help you identify the phase cancellation in your communication—the moments where you clash instead of harmonize—and help you rewrite those scripts for deeper connection.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-[2.25rem] bg-white/90 shadow-[0_18px_45px_rgba(148,163,184,0.5)] px-5 py-5">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-950/90">In-Person Sessions</h3>
              <p class="mt-2.5 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/85">
                I believe healing happens best where you feel most grounded. In-person sessions can be held in nature, a private home, or any quiet space that feels safe and supportive for you. Removing the clinical office environment allows the nervous system to open in its own time.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-[2.25rem] bg-white/90 shadow-[0_18px_45px_rgba(148,163,184,0.5)] px-5 py-5">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-950/90">Remote & Async Coaching</h3>
              <p class="mt-2.5 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/85">
                Presence isn't limited by geography. I offer Virtual Meetings and Asynchronous Voice Coaching for everyone—whether you are across the world or just prefer to process your growth from the comfort of your own space.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="lab" class="mt-12 md:mt-16">
          <h2 class="inline-block text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-indigo-950/90 border-b border-pink-200 pb-1">
            Sound Engineering & The Lab
          </h2>

          <div class="mt-8">
            <div class="float-right ml-4 md:ml-10 mb-4 w-32 h-32 md:w-56 md:h-56 relative group">
              <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-tr from-emerald-200/40 to-sky-300/40 rounded-2xl blur opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-50 transition duration-700"></div>
              <div class="relative h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/40 shadow-lg">
                <Image src={labImg} alt="The Bass Studio Lab" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" />
              </div>
            </div>

            <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/90 leading-relaxed">
              In the JoySomatic Lab, I merge technical precision with creative flow. Whether I am behind the keyboard or the mixing console, the goal is always the same: finding clarity, reducing noise, and creating resonance.
            </p>
            
            <ul class="mt-6 list-disc pl-5 space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/90">
              <li>
                High-resolution audio production, mixing, and mastering for artists and creators, drawing on nearly two decades of experience.
              </li>
              <li>
                Software development and systems architecture, utilizing modern tools to build efficient, reliable solutions for creative and personal growth.
              </li>
              <li>
                A continuous synthesis of technical craft and human wisdom, exploring the intersection of sound, code, and relational health.
              </li>
            </ul>

            <div class="clear-both"></div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="contact" class="mt-12 md:mt-16">
          <h2 class="inline-block text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-indigo-950/90 border-b border-pink-200 pb-1">
            Work With Me
          </h2>

          <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/90">
            <p class="max-w-none">
              I am available for 1:1 coaching, sound production, and technical collaborations.
            </p>
            <p class="max-w-none">
              Email:
              <a href="mailto:jose@joysomatic.com" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full px-5 py-2.5 text-sm md:text-base font-semibold text-indigo-900/90 bg-violet-200/60 hover:bg-violet-200/90 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(196,181,253,0.7)] hover:-translate-y-[1px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out">
                jose@joysomatic.com
              </a>
            </p>
            <p class="space-x-3">
              <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/joysomatic" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-900/85 bg-white/70 hover:bg-sky-50 hover:shadow-[0_10px_26px_rgba(59,130,246,0.55)] hover:-translate-y-[1px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out">LinkedIn</a>
              <span>|</span>
              <a href="https://github.com/joysomatic" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-900/85 bg-white/70 hover:bg-indigo-50 hover:shadow-[0_10px_26px_rgba(129,140,248,0.55)] hover:-translate-y-[1px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out">GitHub</a>
              <span>|</span>
              <a href="https://instagram.com/joysomatic" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-900/85 bg-white/70 hover:bg-pink-50 hover:shadow-[0_10px_26px_rgba(244,114,182,0.55)] hover:-translate-y-[1px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out">Instagram</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>

      <footer class="mt-16 border-t border-violet-100/80 text-center text-xs md:text-sm text-indigo-900/70 py-6 px-4">
        <p>© 2026 JoySomatic – José Oñate Yáñez | Built with Code & Heart</p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>